      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# LongCat AudioDiT TTS\n\n  ## Auto-Download\n\n  **Models auto-download on first run** - no manual setup needed!\n\n  | Model | VRAM | Download Size |\n  |-------|------|---------------|\n  | LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B-bf16 (recommended) | ~12GB | ~7GB |\n  | LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B-fp8 | ~8-12GB | ~4GB |\n  | LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B (fp32) | ~20GB | ~14GB |\n  ---\n\n  ## Manual Download\n\n  | File | Size | Link |\n  |------|------|------|\n  | LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B-bf16 | ~7GB | [Download](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B-bf16) |\n  | LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B-fp8 | ~4GB | [Download](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B-fp8) |\n  | LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B (fp32) | ~14GB | [Download](https://huggingface.co/meituan-longcat/LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B) |\n\n  Place in `ComfyUI/models/audiodit/` as folder names: `LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B-bf16`, `LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B-fp8`, or `LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B`\n\n  ---\n\n  ## FP8 model is dequantized to BF16 at load time using per-tensor scales from fp8_scales.json\n\n  ---\n\n  ## Nodes\n\n  | Node | Description |\n  |------|-------------|\n  | **LongCat AudioDiT TTS** | Basic text-to-speech synthesis |\n  | **LongCat AudioDiT Voice Clone TTS** | Clone voice from 3-15s reference audio |\n  | **LongCat AudioDiT Multi-Speaker TTS** | Multi-speaker dialogue with [speaker_N]: tags |\n\n  ---\n\n  ## Parameters\n\n  | Parameter | Default | Description |\n  |-----------|---------|-------------|\n  | steps | 16 | ODE Euler solver steps (4-64) |\n  | guidance_strength | 4.0 | CFG/APG guidance scale (0-10) |\n  | guidance_method | cfg / apg | cfg for TTS, apg for voice cloning |\n  | dtype | auto | auto, bf16, fp16, fp32 |\n  | attention | auto | auto, sdpa, sage_attention, flash_attention |\n  | keep_model_loaded | true | Cache model + auto-offload to CPU between runs |\n\n  ---\n\n  ## Voice Cloning\n\n  Connect reference audio (3-15 seconds recommended) to `prompt_audio` input. Providing `prompt_text` (transcript) improves quality significantly.\n\n  ---\n\n  ## Multi-Speaker\n\n  Use `[speaker_N]:` tags in text:\n  [speaker_1]: Hello, welcome to the show!\n  [speaker_2]: Thanks for having me!\n  [speaker_1]: Let's get started.\n\n  ---\n\n  ## Links\n\n  - Original [LongCat-AudioDiT](https://github.com/meituan-longcat/LongCat-AudioDiT)\n  - Models [3.5B](https://huggingface.co/meituan-longcat/LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B) / [3.5B-bf16](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B-bf16) / [3.5B-fp8](https://huggingface.co/drbaph/LongCat-AudioDiT-3.5B-fp8)\n  - Issues [Report Bug](https://github.com/Saganaki22/ComfyUI-LongCat-AudioDIT-TTS/issues)"
      ],
      "color": "#c09430",
      "bgcolor": "rgba(24,24,27,.9)"
    },
